Introduction

Dosie is a South Korean signer and dancer signed with RBW. She is the Main Dancer and Sub Vocalist of the girl group PURPLE KISS and was the first member to join RBW in 2016. She participated in the idol survival show MIXNINE, where she finished 78th.

She debuted with PURPLE KISS on March 15, 2021, with the mini album “INTO VIOLET”, with the title track “Ponzona”.
